headline.print_headline: 9 Killed, 10 Missing in Sri Lanka Mudslides
headline.main: 9 Killed, 10 Missing in Sri Lanka Mudslides

lead_paragraph: At least nine people were killed and 10 others were missing in mudslides triggered by heavy rains Friday in the central hills of Sri Lanka, officials said.
